OL,3,C'It is the saddest thing':
OL,4,CMisinterpreted ECG tests result in
OL,5,Cfatal consequences
OL,7,FITV News reporter Lauren Hall speaks
OL,8,Fto a mother who says her daughter's
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest "could have been
OL,10,Fprevented"
OL,12,FITV Regional News has been told a
OL,13,F"concerning" number of patients have
OL,14,Fdied from heart conditions after their
OL,15,Ftest results were misinterpreted by
OL,16,Fmedical professionals.
OL,18,FClarissa Nicholls, a student at the
OL,19,FUniversity of Cambridge, collapsed and
OL,20,Fdied while hiking with a friend in
OL,21,FFrance last year.
