OL,3,C'It is the saddest thing':
OL,4,CMisinterpreted ECG tests result in
OL,5,Cfatal consequences
OL,7,FShe was a keen athlete with a passion
OL,8,Ffor running and hockey.
OL,10,FHer mother, Hilary Nicholls, told ITV
OL,11,FNews that her daughter was "incredibly
OL,12,Fsporty", "hugely dynamic" and "had so
OL,13,Fmuch energy".
OL,15,F"She was the model of someone who was
OL,16,Ffit and healthy but she had no idea
OL,17,Fthat there was something wrong."
