OL,3,C'It is the saddest thing':
OL,4,CMisinterpreted ECG tests result in
OL,5,Cfatal consequences
OL,7,FThe only clue had been the year before
OL,8,Fher death when she collapsed while
OL,9,Fplaying sport, Nicholls said of her
OL,10,Fdaughter.
OL,12,FShe had an ECG to check her heart but
OL,13,Fthe test results were not looked at by
OL,14,Fa specialist.
OL,16,FThis meant a rare heart condition was
OL,17,Fnot picked up and Clarissa did not
OL,18,Frealise that exercising was actually
OL,19,Fputting her life at risk.
