OL,3,C'It is the saddest thing':
OL,4,CMisinterpreted ECG tests result in
OL,5,Cfatal consequences
OL,7,FThe Chief Executive of Cardiac Risk in
OL,8,Fthe Young, Dr Steven Cox, said: "One
OL,9,Fof the greatest tragedies is when a
OL,10,Fyoung person presents with symptoms,
OL,11,Fthey've gone for medical care, they've
OL,12,Fhad an ECG and then they've been
OL,13,Freassured and told that everything is
OL,14,Ffine and they've gone home, and then
OL,15,Fthere's been a subsequent sudden
OL,16,Fcardiac death or cardiac arrest."
OL,18,FHe explained ECGs should be looked at
OL,19,Fby specialists but that often does not
OL,20,Fhappen.
OL,26,@pD@aOUxD@aO]
