OL,3,C'It is the saddest thing':
OL,4,CMisinterpreted ECG tests result in
OL,5,Cfatal consequences
OL,7,FITV News approached NHS England who
OL,8,Fsaid training for clinical
OL,9,Fprofessionals on how to interpret ECGs
OL,10,Fdoesn't fall within their remit.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care said: "Patient
OL,14,Fsafety is of utmost importance and we
OL,15,Fexpect guidance on assessing
OL,16,Felectrocardiograms to be followed at
OL,17,Fall times and for all clinicians
OL,18,Freviewing ECGs to have received the
OL,19,Fappropriate training.
OL,26,@uD@^OU
