OL,3,C'It is the saddest thing':
OL,4,CMisinterpreted ECG tests result in
OL,5,Cfatal consequences
OL,7,FProfessor Michael Papadakis said it
OL,8,Fcould be a "game-changer", explaining:
OL,9,F"With reliable A.I. algorithms, it may
OL,10,Fwell be that we are able to take a
OL,11,Fpicture of that particular ECG on our
OL,12,Fphone and, through an application,
OL,13,Fmake an instantaneous interpretation
OL,14,Fwhich can give us what we call
OL,15,Fdifferential diagnoses ` a list of
OL,16,Fdiagnoses of what may be wrong with
OL,17,Four patient that the doctor can act on.
